  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501480/extras/660df1102ff0cc3255cc429ab316219b.avif?t=1611167638\" width=392 height=93 /></span><br><br>Hey! Are you ready to start a new life? A new place, new people, and some unique new friends... Enough to start a great adventure!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501480/extras/6ef6f851e00421b04c26eb729e779453.avif?t=1611167638\" width=392 height=93 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Meet Léo, a very friendly fan of manga and anime.<br></li><li>There is Lucille, a nice and cool person. Maybe you'll fall in love with her...<br></li><li>Ethan, a very popular boy with a tempered character. Will you be friend with him?<br></li><li>And then Emi, she is Léo's cousin and she also is in high school. She is quite the character!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501480/extras/660df1102ff0cc3255cc429ab316219b.avif?t=1611167638\" width=392 height=93 /></span><br><br>Hey! Are you ready to start a new life? A new place, new people, and some unique new friends... Enough to start a great adventure!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501480/extras/6ef6f851e00421b04c26eb729e779453.avif?t=1611167638\" width=392 height=93 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Meet Léo, a very friendly fan of manga and anime.<br></li><li>There is Lucille, a nice and cool person. Maybe you'll fall in love with her...<br></li><li>Ethan, a very popular boy with a tempered character. Will you be friend with him?<br></li><li>And then Emi, she is Léo's cousin and she also is in high school. She is quite the character!</li></ul>",
